<main class="container">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="label">Cluster · 09 · Sacred Calendar &amp; Aztec Cosmos</div>
    <h1>Nahui Ollin</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Four Movement &nbsp;·&nbsp; The Fifth Sun &nbsp;·&nbsp; The World That Ends in Earthquake</p>
    <div class="divider">◈ ◈ ◈</div>
    <p>The Aztec cosmos ran on interlocking calendars — a 260-day sacred round, a 365-day solar year, a 52-year binding cycle. This cluster is ten apps that compute, reveal, and perform that system: calendar tools that actually work and myth interfaces that put you inside the cosmology.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Sacred Round</div>
      <div class="v">260 Days</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Solar Year</div>
      <div class="v">365 Days</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Calendar Round</div>
      <div class="v">52 Years</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Creation Eras</div>
      <div class="v">Five Suns</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-label section-label--gold">Calendar Tools</div>

  <section class="apps">
    {{#each calendarApps}}
      <article class="app {{#if live}}app--live{{else}}app--pending{{/if}} app--{{accent}}">
        <div class="head">
          <span class="num">№ {{num}} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{slug}}</span>
          <span class="status">{{#if live}}Inscribed{{else}}Pending{{/if}}</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
        <p class="tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
        {{#if live}}
          <a class="shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{title}} screenshot">
            <img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';" />
          </a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Consult</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Mirror</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Reshape</a>
          </div>
          <a class="prompt-link" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">◈ start fresh from this prompt</a>
        {{else}}
          <div class="shot"><div class="shot-placeholder">Awaiting Inscription</div></div>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">Start From Prompt</a>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </article>
    {{/each}}
  </section>

  <hr class="codex-divider" />

  <div class="section-label section-label--jade">Myth &amp; Oracle</div>

  <section class="apps">
    {{#each oracleApps}}
      <article class="app {{#if live}}app--live{{else}}app--pending{{/if}} app--{{accent}}">
        <div class="head">
          <span class="num">№ {{num}} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{slug}}</span>
          <span class="status">{{#if live}}Inscribed{{else}}Pending{{/if}}</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
        <p class="tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
        {{#if live}}
          <a class="shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{title}} screenshot">
            <img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';" />
          </a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Consult</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Mirror</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Reshape</a>
          </div>
          <a class="prompt-link" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">◈ start fresh from this prompt</a>
        {{else}}
          <div class="shot"><div class="shot-placeholder">Awaiting Inscription</div></div>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">Start From Prompt</a>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </article>
    {{/each}}
  </section>

  <section class="epilogue">
    <h2>◈ Codex Note</h2>
    <p>The Aztec calendar was not a metaphor. It was a computational system that governed every undertaking — when to plant, when to fight, when to build a temple, when to fear the dark. These apps run the same numbers, drawn from the same anchor points. The fifth sun still moves.</p>
  </section>
</main>

